  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK496">
<l>kaṭalōṭā kālva ṉeṭuntēr kaṭalōṭu</l>
<l>nāvāyu mōṭā nilattu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Wide chariots, with mighty wheels, will not run on the ocean; neither will ships that the traverse ocean, move on the earth.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
